    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏介绍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《召唤师崛起》是一款俯视角角色扮演游戏，玩家将扮演一个被电脑吸入异世界的角色，从此踏上回家之路的故事 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家拥有多个技能和几十种不同的装备，装备的特殊词条将直接影响技能的效果，甚至改变原有的技能形态而变得更强大，通过装备搭配技能，体验不一样的战斗风格吧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/722dcc2ad61351530a4b49e64ff05655.poster.avif?t=1754151545\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/722dcc2ad61351530a4b49e64ff05655.webm?t=1754151545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/722dcc2ad61351530a4b49e64ff05655.mp4?t=1754151545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样的法术效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/42e66a91317494a33bc15ed197b6be97.poster.avif?t=1754151545\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/42e66a91317494a33bc15ed197b6be97.webm?t=1754151545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/42e66a91317494a33bc15ed197b6be97.mp4?t=1754151545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机多样的宝箱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/d379ca2f543b576b2e7164b6b4f22587.poster.avif?t=1754151545\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a